{"tid":1604811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"古圖爾斯：你地唔識波！","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:41:06.000Z","uid":226925,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f408e2f7247874979af531eae9588a5023c0f94","tid":1604811,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"Now Sports-體育】皇家馬德里門將古圖奧斯於周六西甲馬德里打吡保持0失球，賽後暗嘲批評他的人不懂足球。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里作客以0:0賽和同市宿敵馬德里體育會，除了以7戰4勝3和15分繼續排在榜首之外，更是教練施丹兩度執教下，首次連續3場比賽保持清白之身；皇馬之前以分別以1:0、2:0擊敗西維爾、奧沙辛拿。<br />\n<br />\n古圖奧斯（Thibaut Courtois）在2018年加盟皇馬後，一直被批評表現不濟。他在這3場比賽，對馬體會及西維爾皆正選披甲，當中鬥床單兵團更是倒戈相向，可說是吐氣揚眉。<br />\n<br />\n對於周中被新兵阿希奧拿頂替及種種批評聲音，這名27歲比利時國腳說：「這不會影響我。我只會跟懂得足球的人分析自己的比賽，我只會跟我的教練及隊友討論。」"},{"pid":"6e124c35de9a4eedd70ca2a3d94bf80c759e31e0","tid":1604811,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d532ac29237f6e6cbbb18c43c307576662b355aa","tid":1604811,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"🐍"},{"pid":"da5f5e71b22c973e9be5c90e3a54752189979ec9","tid":1604811,"uid":25758,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"龍門既野<br />\n一係救到   一係救唔到<br />\n你呢幾場0失球咪比你威下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d42dedfe838cc919905159ed524e6f9350854cb","tid":1604811,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"我地呢到大把學界高手話你廢"},{"pid":"456f4409e021cb8e4623216fce2fc66d9255dffb","tid":1604811,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7256b6c8f51c970d0f5dc6aae1f9986f63a9f4c3","tid":1604811,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d42dedfe838cc919905159ed524e6f9350854cb","tid":16048